            <p>The application features an intuitive and user-friendly interface that allows you to 
            navigate your collection effortlessly. It provides clear options for adding, editing, searching, and deleting entries.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-dark text-white border rounded-3">
            <h2>Add Games</h2>
            <p>For each game, you can input the following details:
                <ul>
                <li>Title: The name of the board game.</li>
                <li>Game Description: A brief description or overview of the game.</li>
                <li>Number of Players: The minimum and maximum number of players required to play the game.</li>
                <li>Year of Release: The year when the game was originally released.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

